HEADWORD: Prolixious
<hw>Pro*lix"ious</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Dilatory;
tedious; superfluous.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> ⟦ldquo⟧Lay by all
nicety, and <xex>prolixious</xex> blushes.⟦rdquo⟧
